<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 28 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Dance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天就是翘首以盼的万圣节！<delay frames="50" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />或许你在做准备的时候遇到了不少困难，<delay20 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天可以痛痛快快玩耍，<delay20 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />把前面的辛劳抵消。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 28 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天是万圣节，<delay8 />
我想你一定已经准备得很完美了吧<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果还有什么让你挂心的事，<delay8 />
现在离活动开始还有一些时间，<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你快去完成它吧。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 28 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天的万圣节活动
到底会举办成什么样子呢，<delay8 />真期待呀～<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />即便已经是一个成熟的大人，每次一有活动，<delay8 />
我还是可以和大家一起踊跃参与。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真幸福啊，<delay20 />能够生活在这座<tag a="110" b="32" />上。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哎呀，<delay20 />万圣节活动<delay8 />
马上就要开始了！<delay frames="50" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不要忘了做好心理准备哦。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哎呀，讨厌<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我也差不多
该去乔装打扮了。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />还得重新化妆，<delay frames="30" /><anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真忙呀～</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />万圣节活动即将开幕<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我们都要尽情享受节日乐趣，<delay8 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />留下美好的回忆啊。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="100" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">你知道<tag a="110" b="32" />上多了一些
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />用南瓜做成的<delay8 />装饰品吗？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那肯定是因为万圣节的缘故啦。
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />虽然不知道是谁的行为，<delay20 />
但我们身边居然有这么一个
讲究仪式感的朋友呀～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">你有没有感觉<delay20 />这座<tag a="110" b="32" />上的南瓜装饰<delay8 />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />开始逐渐增加了？<pageBreak /><anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />估计是因为日子一天天接近了吧。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我也开始像个小孩一样<delay8 />
觉得心情激动啦。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="102" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我说，<delay20 />你有发现吗？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />南瓜装饰好像<delay8 />真的多起来了？<pageBreak /><anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />总感觉<delay8 />那个南瓜的眼神
好像能看穿我脑海里的某个部分，<delay20 />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />感觉有点可怕啊。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="103" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我说真的，<tag a="110" b="32" />上的南瓜装饰<delay8 />
会不会有些太多了？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />似乎大家真的很期待万圣节到来啊。
<anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />怎么说呢，<delay8 />我也很期待能收到
你给我的糖果，<delay8 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以也算理解这种心情吧～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>